Private Events
The Canopy West Palm Beach Hotel offers over 8,000 square feet of combined space for private dining and special events in Downtown West Palm Beach. Stylish interiors, fantastic food and great service meet to create a memorable experience. We feature 7 unique private event spaces such as our rooftop bar, ground floor restaurant, and our beautiful ballroom with four private meeting rooms.
For all inquiries, please fill out the form below or email
Krista.Smith@Hilton.com
and we’ll be in touch soon.
View Menu
Inquire Now
Treehouse Rooftop
The Treehouse Rooftop bar is a magical oasis perched atop the West Palm Beach skyline. Guests can take in the beautiful sunsets of Downtown West Palm Beach while standing poolside or lounging by the restaurant's high-energy bar and dining room.
Click on the image to view a photo gallery of each space.
Capacity:
Indoor Seating: 72 | Outdoor Seating: 20 Beds & 12 Seats
Banyan Ballroom
The Banyan Ballroom, offers an impressive 3,069 sq. ft. with floor to ceiling windows and unique partial glass walls. Just outside the ballroom you will find 1,500 sq. ft. of flexible pre-function space known as The Glass Foyer, perfect for cocktail receptions, wedding ceremonies and so much more! Let us guide you in selecting the ideal wedding, meeting, or events package offering customized catering menus with an expert events team offering unmatched service, and stylish backdrops for your special event.
Click on the image to view a photo gallery of each space.
Capacity:
Standing: 340 | Seated: 180
Meeting Rooms
The hotel's convenient location and stunning space creates the perfect home to host your meetings. Our Banyan Ballroom offers 3,069 sq. ft. of space that can be divided into smaller spaces to fit your meeting needs. The elegantly modern meeting rooms can accommodate board meetings, tradeshows, trainings and executive retreats.
Click on the image to view a photo gallery of each space.
Capacity:
Varies depending on room set up.

About Us
We're a magical oasis located on the 13th floor of the Canopy West Palm Beach hotel with a view of the West Palm skyline.  On the weekends, the space becomes the premiere daytime poolside hang and then transforms to an evening cocktail lounge with top DJs spinning the night away.
